name: I Became the Academys Disabled Student
summary:
I created a game character.
Instead of taking several perks, I added restrictions.Restriction (I): Curse of Sensory Seal
Permanently seals a chosen sense.
Choice: Sight, Taste, SmellRestriction (II): Curse of Short Life
You are born with a body doomed to a short life.Restriction (III): Curse of Silence
Speaking causes you pain.When the next day came, I couldnt see anything.
